Long promo: 

Steeping instructions for a perfect cup of 🍵 every time.

Description:

Simple application listing instructions for steeping different tea types. Includes guides for temperature 🌡, steeping time 🕰, and good practices. It also lets you quickly setup an appropriate timer ⏲ in system default stopwatch app. Supports both Fahrenheit and Celsius units. 

Long description:

Simple application listing instructions for steeping different tea types. Includes guides for temperature 🌡, steeping time 🕰, and good practices. It also lets you quickly setup an appropriate timer ⏲ in system default stopwatch app. Supports both Fahrenheit and Celsius units.

I plan to add support for Wear OS smart watches soon ⌚️.

Contact me directly if you have any questions, suggestions or general feedback 📬. More contact information can be found at my personal website - https://morningbird.eu. 

I read every review to make it better 😘. If you are a tea lover too, please leave a ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ rating.
